Draw an arc.



```js
arc(data: ArcData, sketch_group: SketchGroup, tag?: String) -> SketchGroup
```

### Examples

```js
const exampleSketch = startSketchOn('XZ')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([10, 0], %)
  |> arc({
       angle_start: 0,
       angle_end: 280,
       radius: 16
     }, %)
  |> close(%)
```
